# - Set variables
# - Create aliases
# - Customize the prompt
# - Write handy functions
# - Change ZSH options
# - Adjust history functionality
# - Improve line editor (completions, menu, navigation, etc.)
# - Add locations to $PATH variable (or $path array)
# - Use ZSH plugins
# - Change key bindings
# - Add "zstyles" for completions & more

